\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">設定為應用程式啟用伺服器端渲染功能所需的提供程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Sets up providers necessary to enable server rendering functionality for the application.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/provideServerRendering\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideServerRendering</a></span>(): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <p>沒有引數。</p>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">一組用於設定伺服器的提供程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code>: A set of providers to setup the server.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/provideServerRendering#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">如何嚮應用程式新增伺服器支援的基本範例：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Basic example of how you can add server support to your application:</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(AppComponent, {\n  providers: [<a href=\"api/platform-server/provideServerRendering\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideServerRendering</a>()]\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-server\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/EnvironmentProviders\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/provideServerRendering#provideserverrendering\n - api/platform-server/provideServerRendering#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-server/src/provide_server.ts?message=docs(platform-server)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L13-L44\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-server/src/provide_server.ts#L13-L44\n-->"}